9月3日，本季第一个热带气旋在[[巴哈马|巴哈马]]和[[百慕大|百慕大]]之间的中途海域附近出现<ref name="HURDAT" />。附近一艘船只的观测纪录估计风速为每小时130公里，表明气旋强度达到飓风标准<ref name="1xls">{{cite web | author = Hurricane Research Division | year = 2010 | title = Track data for Storm #1 in 1868 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | accessdate = 2016-12-01 | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/excelfiles_centerfix/1868_1.xls | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304041134/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/excelfiles_centerfix/1868_1.xls | format = [[Microsoft_Excel|XLS]] | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。风暴起初向北移动，于9月4日在百慕大以西约355公里洋面经过。接下来飓风转向东北，<ref name="HURDAT" />“约翰·理查森号”（{{lang|en|John Richardson}}）于9月5日遇到[[烈风|烈风]]强度风力，致使船上装载的货物落水<ref name="year" />。根据呼号为“格林诺克”（{{lang|en|Greenock}}）的船只记载，气象学家估计风暴于9月6日在[[新斯科舍|新斯科舍]][[哈利法克斯|哈利法克斯]]东南方向约640公里海域达到[[最大持续风速|持续风速]]每小时165公里的最高强度，在现代[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]下属二级飓风标准{{#tag:ref|[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]于1971年面世<ref name="USA Today">{{cite news | author = Jack Williams | title = Hurricane scale invented to communicate storm danger | publisher = [[今日美国|USA Today]] | date = 2005-05-17 | accessdate = 2013-08-04 | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/weather/hurricane/whscale.htm | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160324154907/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/weather/hurricane/whscale.htm | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-24 }}</ref>，再对[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]大西洋飓风数据库的所有风暴追溯分级<ref>{{cite report | publisher = Hurricane Research Division | title = Chronological List of All Continental United States Hurricanes: 1851-2012 | date = 2013-06 | accessdate = 2016-11-10 | archivedate = 2016-05-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160503012801/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/All_U.S._Hurricanes.html | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/All_U.S._Hurricanes.html }}</ref>。|group="注"}}<ref name="1xls" />。该船受到持续14小时的狂风袭击，导致船长和另一名船员丧生<ref name="year" />。气旋转向东北，最终从[[纽芬兰岛|纽芬兰岛]]南面经过后于9月7日失去踪影<ref name="HURDAT" />。
